<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Cog</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-19 16:22:53</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>1) Sash will work from level 1 (per gordan wrynn)<BR>
2) It does not proc, it is a permanent effect.<BR>
3) The haste % is a bit less then Cloak of Flames which is 25% my educated guess is around 18-19%<BR>
4) Any monk should own one, it is a silly notion that any monk would think otherwise. Anything that will increase the speed of a monks meele is worth its price in gold.<BR>
<BR>
The spawn and loot is totaly random. you wont see the frenzied ghoul in days, even weeks,  then you will have 4 pop in 3 hours all but one with sashes (witnessed that one)<BR>
<BR>
He conned blue to me at 44 <BR>
we held area with a group of 40's<BR>
cleric,enchanter,warrior(2) and rouge.<BR>
make sure to bring enchanter with you, I give props to that kick ass class.<BR>
<BR>
Good luck to all who seek this item<BR>
<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
