<BR>
(1) Necro, you are a dumbass and are obviously lying, considering the sash is lore and you quote got a "few."<BR>
Probably just a newbie trying to screw with everyone, don't get so worked up about it.<BR>
<BR>
(2) Whoever left their name blank and suggested that people " /em Humps the Frenzied Ghoul to death." is a pervert, that doesn't work, he is a moron.<BR>
<BR>
(3) This is a MUST HAVE item for any tank, if you ever get to any decently high level, trust me, you will have one. It lowers the delay in your weapon immensely, but if you have a lower delay weapon it is harder to notice. Get a VERY high delay weapon and you will see the difference right away. <BR>
<BR>
(4) If you are looking for one, do a /who of the major guilds on your server, someone is always raiding L guk (Will appear as Gukbottom).<BR>
<BR>
(5) For any monks, just a little tidbit, lowers your punch delay from 36 to 30.<BR>
<BR>
Hope that clears a few things up.<BR>
